description: Winter wheat, sown in the autumn/winter, except in 2015 and 2020 when spring wheat was sown, as wet conditions in the autumn/winter prevented the sowing of winter wheat.
Spring wheat, sown in the spring of 2015 and 2020, instead of the usual winter wheat, as wet conditions in the autumn/winter prevented the sowing of the usual winter wheat variety
Bare fallow, no crop, used to control weeds on Section 8 (no herbicides applied) when necessary. Received FYM, castor meal and PKNaMg fertilizers but no fertilizer N.
